data.description: Located in a beautiful cul de sac this home features 3 way split floor plan along with an open space concept, large kitchen island, walk in pantry, 36" cabinets along with 18x18 tile throughout home blinds along with appliances included great home for entertaining and no rear neighbors!  Close to Hwy 27, 30 minutes from Attractions!
